title: FireBootCamp - Sydney Gala
eventShortDescription:
Gala Event for the FireBootCampers from the June​​ Intake​
​​
If you're looking for a developer who is so passionate about coding they take 9 weeks out of their life to do nothing but code, then you need to be at our Gala morning tea. This morning is for employers to see the web applications our Boot Campers have developed over the 9 weeks, and have a chance to speak to them. After 9 weeks of intense training, these "FireBootCampers" are the best candidates on the market. Come along, meet the guys and put an offer in for the developer you want. Strike while the iron's hot!​
